skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: baby care
des:
Baby care skill is designed to help new parents to run a quick diaper bag checklist at any time they are packing or on their way out so they can make sure they got everything they need for their baby when they are out! 
Just say "Alexa, ask baby care to run a diaper bag checklist for my six months old baby" 
or
"Alexa, ask baby care to run a diaper bag checklist as I am heading to the beach/ mall/ park"
or simply say 
"Alexa, open baby care" 
We will be adding new features soon!!
